subject: Football
Playoff Games
lead_paragraph: Kansas City, winner of 11 straight, looks to upset New England in Saturday’s early game, followed by Green Bay-Arizona. On Sunday, Seattle plays at Carolina, and Pittsburgh is at Denver.
